data.description: VERY SPACIOUS! This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, two-car garage, and fenced in yard.  Cozy and beautiful wood-burning fireplace in the living room (also has a gas line).  Wood and tile floors throughout.  Separate dining room next to a spacious kitchen.  The basement is partially finished with a bonus room or office.  Covered deck is perfect for enjoyment. All appliances stay.
